hundertwasser_comment_ge-'Ich war schon sehr in Venedig zu Hause, wu&Atilde;te, da&Atilde; die Gondeln asymmetrisch sind und bin bei Aqua alta in Gummistiefeln im hohen Wasser spazierengegangen. An der Caf&Atilde;&copy;bar mu&Atilde;te man aufpassen, da&Atilde; das Wechselgeld nicht ins Wasser f&Atilde;&curren;llt. Wenn abends die Lichter der Laternen und vollerleuchteten Gesch&Atilde;&curren;fte, die alle offen waren, sich in den Wasserwellen, in den Stra&Atilde;en spiegelten, glaubte ich mich wie Alice im Wunderland.',
hundertwasser_comment_en-'I was already very much at home in Venice, knew that the gondolas are asymmetrical and went for walks in rubber boots in the high water at aqua alta [Italian for high water]. At the caf&Atilde;&copy; bar you had to look out that your change didn&#039;t fall into the water. When in the evening the lights of the lanterns and fully illuminated shops, all of which were open, were reflected in the water&#039;s waves, in the streets, it seemed as if I were Alice in Wonderland.',
